Usage: get_library_set [-help] <libSetName> {-timing | -si | -aocv | -socv }

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<libSetName>       # #Specifies the name of the library set (string, required)
-aocv              # Returns the aocv library names for the specified library
                   # set (bool, optional)
-si                # Returns the cdb library names for the specified library
                   # set (bool, optional)
-socv              # Returns the socv library names for the specified library
                   # set (bool, optional)
-timing            # Returns the timing library names for the specified library
                   # set (bool, optional)